<p><strong>Languages</strong> Draconic</p>

<p><strong>Challenge</strong> 4 (1,100 XP)</p>

<p><strong>Actions</strong></p>

<p><strong><em>Bite.</em></strong> Melee Weapon Attack: +6 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 9 (1d10 + 4) piercing damage plus 3 (1d6) fire damage.</p>

<p><strong><em>Fire Breath (Recharge 5-6).</em></strong> The dragon exhales fire in a 15-foot cone. Each creature in that area must make a DC l3 Dexterity saving throw, taking 24 (7d6) fire damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p>

